About
Murray Charles & Sons Plumbing is located at the address 1319 Sleepy Hollow Dr in Dallas, Texas 75235.  They can be contacted via phone at (214) 630-5479 for pricing, hours and directions.  Murray Charles & Sons Plumbing specializes in Bathrooms, Heating & Cooling, Showers.  Murray Charles & Sons Plumbing has an annual sales volume of 0 - 500K.  .For more information contact Charles  Murray, OwnerMurray Charles & Sons Plumbing provides Pump Repairs, Duct Cleaning, Residential Services to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Murray Charles & Sons Plumbing view the map to the right.  For reviews of Murray Charles & Sons Plumbing see below.









